channel.title: Can't compile any clients(Don't just overlook this please.)
channel.description: Hello, I have tried to compile about 30 different clients of various bases.(Delta, Project Insanity, Dodian and Hyperion.) ALL of them threw errors related to the signlink class. I'm convinced this is a Java issue and not just a client error. Could someone please help me, I have started development on a clean Project Insanity and I would like to be able to compile my client aswell as my source. Thank you in advance.
